(43, 'How to Price Your Product or Service Just Right', '', 0, 41, 'How to Price Your Product or Service Just Right.pdf', '<p><strong>\"The Best Strategies for Pricing Your Product Competitively!\"</strong></p>', 1323147600, 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, '', '', '', 0, 'http://', 0, 3, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 800, 600, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<p> </p>\r\n<p>If you are trying to sell something on the Internet, pricing your services/ products would be the single most important decision you will take. Since, the Internet provides thousands of alternatives to the customers, you need to be at par with the competition. The prices that you quite will determine how long you can stay in the market.</p>\r\n<p>You need to acquire a clear cut idea about pricing. To what extent can you push it? How often do you need to review the prices? A lot would depend on how you handle this stage of business.</p>\r\n<p>You have to pinpoint a consumer group to begin with and then estimate how much they would be willing to pay for your services or products.</p>\r\n<p>Sneak Peak: Table Of Contents</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Pricing: All You Need to Know 5</li>\r\n<li>Working With Price Sensitive Buyers 7</li>\r\n<li>How to Achieve \"Winning Price\" 9</li>\r\n<li>Pricing According to the Type of Product 11</li>\r\n<li>Pricing Strategies That Improve Profit 13</li>\r\n<li>Price Skimming As a Pricing Strategy 15</li>\r\n<li>Is Psychological Pricing an Effective Strategy? 17</li>\r\n<li>Market Penetration Pricing 19</li>\r\n<li>Promotional Pricing 21</li>\r\n<li>Competitive Pricing 22</li>\r\n<li>Offering Discounts as a Part of Your Pricing Strategy 23</li>\r\n<li>Alternative Pricing Strategies 25</li>\r\n<li>Change Prices to Make Your Offerings More Appealing in Non-Price Ways 27</li>\r\n<li>Value Based Pricing 29</li>\r\n<li>How To Know If Your Pricing Is Right? 30</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 'ecommerce', '', 0, '0=0', 1, 2, '', 0, 1, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', '', 0, 0),
